        {
            "title": "半日收市｜港股半日跌322點   晶片股逆市升  資源股捱沽",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股半日挫322點，曾跌376點，龍頭科網成跌市元兇，晶片股跑贏，資源股跑輸，中國人壽(02628)績優，收升近半成。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國人壽官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240425_FI_source-web_02388-8.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國人壽官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240425_FI_source-web_02388-8.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國人壽官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數半日報25789，跌322點或1.23%，今早開市報26008點，跌103點或0.4%，最高見26072，僅跌39點或0.14%，中段低見25735，挫376點或1.44%，為半日低位。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數半日報4862，跌48點或0.98%，今早開報4876點，跌33點或0.68%；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生國企指數半日報8693，跌112點或1/28%，今早以8757點開市，跌47點或0.54%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交1565.85億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指報25657，跌283點或1.09% ; 科指期貨半日報4867，趺45點或0.92%，高水5點，國指期貨半日報8666，跌102點或1.16%，低水27點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">晶片股跑贏，中芯國際(00981)升6.38%，報70元，貢獻恒指27點，為表現最佳藍籌股 ; 華虹半導體(01347)升3.89%，報112.3元，成交入20大。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國人壽(02628)半日升4.89%，報28.74元，首季新業務價值升75.5%勝預期，今早公布季績的友邦(01299)則先升後跌，最高見87.15元，升2.58%，半日收跌0.24%，報84.75元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">資源股跑輸，中國宏橋(01378)報32.74元，跌4.49%，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 洛陽鉬業(03993)跌3.78%，報17.58元 ; 紫金礦業(02899)跌2.3%，報35.62元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">科網股拖低大市，阿里巴巴(09988)挫3.22%，報126.4元，影響恒指64點；騰訊(00700)報464.8元，拖低恒指58點 ; 小米(01810)半日跌3.72%，報29.02元。三股成跌市主力。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">長飛光纖(06869)半日瀉11.87%，報203.4元，成交居第五位，公司公布首季多賺226.4%，至4.95億元人民幣，績後股價大幅回吐。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15943025-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e8%b7%8c322%e9%bb%9e-%e6%99%b6%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%87-%e8%b3%87%e6%ba%90%e8%82%a1%e6%8d%b1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-8.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-30 12:25:20",
