            "title": "內地4 月PMI報50.3%  低於上月",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國家統計局公布，4月份製造業採購經理指數為50.3%，略低於上月0.1個百分點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20240304_FI_source-ap_china-economy_fb.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20240304_FI_source-ap_china-economy_fb.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">非製造業商務活動指數為49.4%，比上月下降0.7個百分點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">綜合PMI產出指數為50.1%，比上月下降0.4個百分點，仍高於臨界點。<br/> <br/> </p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15942056-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b04-%e6%9c%88pmi%e5%a0%b150-3-%e4%bd%8e%e6%96%bc%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88",
