            "title": "人行今進行1262億人幣逆回購 淨投放1257億",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">人民銀行今日在公開市場進行1262億元(人民幣‧下同)的7天期逆回購操作，操作利率1.40%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">計入今日有5億元逆回購到期，人行在公開市場今日淨投放1257億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15942045-%e4%ba%ba%e8%a1%8c%e4%bb%8a%e9%80%b2%e8%a1%8c1262%e5%84%84%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3%e9%80%86%e5%9b%9e%e8%b3%bc-%e6%b7%a8%e6%8a%95%e6%94%be1257%e5%84%84",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250507_FI_source-ap_PBC-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-30 09:32:33",
